    (OPEN_BRACE) 
        (CONST) 
            (identifier, quarters) 
            (number, 6) 
        (CONST) 
            (identifier, dimes) 
            (number, 3) 
        (CONST) 
            (identifier, nickels) 
            (number, 7) 
        (CONST) 
            (identifier, pennies) 
            (number, 17) 
        (CONST) 
            (identifier, value) 
            (ADD) 
                (ADD) 
                    (ADD) 
                        (MULTIPLY) 
                            (identifier, quarters) 
                            (number, 25) 
                        (MULTIPLY) 
                            (identifier, dimes) 
                            (number, 10) 
                    (MULTIPLY) 
                        (identifier, nickels) 
                        (number, 5) 
                (identifier, pennies) 
        (PRINT) 
            (identifier, value) 
            (NEWLINE) 
        (CONST) 
            (identifier, ncoins) 
            (ADD) 
                (ADD) 
                    (ADD) 
                        (identifier, quarters) 
                        (identifier, dimes) 
                    (identifier, nickels) 
                (identifier, pennies) 
        (PRINT) 
            (identifier, ncoins) 
            (NEWLINE)

            (identifier, moredimes) 
            (GREATER) 
                (identifier, dimes) 
                (identifier, nickels)

            (identifier, moredimes) 
            (NEWLINE)

            (identifier, boot) 
            (TRUE) 
        (CONST) 
            (identifier, boof) 
            (FALSE)
